  "title": "Motschen's Better Leaves (Programmer Art Edition)",
  "description": "Improves the appearance of leaves with high mod compatibility and performance – now with Programmer Art textures!",
  "body": "<center><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Better Leaves adds additional layers to leaf blocks, making them appear more bushy, dense and natural.</span></p>\n <img src=\"https://github.com/TeamMidnightDust/BetterLeavesLite/blob/dev/banner_p.png?raw=true\" alt=\"A banner showing a leaf block with the text 'Better Leaves Performance Update'\"></img>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Version 9.0 is focused on performance, with textures being automatically created for every leaf. Unlike 8.1, this is not dynamic, so you have to follow a few simple steps to compile custom versions for use with texturepacks. I have already done so for Minecraft's Programmer Art textures.</span></p>\n\n<iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/RL_--nShJ9w\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>I strongly recommend installing the <a href=\"https://www.modrinth.com/mod/cull-leaves\" rel=\"nofollow\">Cull Leaves</a> mod alongside Sodium/Embeddium to get more FPS.</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/QXePegVz/images/388e3d201568ccb6bdaeaa6e0eedf3864bbe83d9.webp\" width=\"842\" height=\"219\" /></p>\n</center>\n\n<details>\n<summary>Explicitly supported Mods (v9.5):</summary>\n\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/ad-astra\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ad Astra</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/alexs-caves\" rel=\"nofollow\">Alex's Caves</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/architects-palette\" rel=\"nofollow\">Architect's Palette</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/ars-elemental\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Ars Elemental</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/ars-nouveau\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Ars Nouveau</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/aurorasdecorations\" rel=\"nofollow\">Aurora's Decorations</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/betterend\" rel=\"nofollow\">Better End</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/betternether\" rel=\"nofollow\">Better Nether</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/bewitchment\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bewitchment</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/biome-makeover\" rel=\"nofollow\">Biome Makeover</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/biomes-o-plenty\" rel=\"nofollow\">Biomes O' Plenty</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/blockus\" rel=\"nofollow\">Blockus</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/blossom\" rel=\"nofollow\">Blossom</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/blue-skies\" rel=\"nofollow\">Blue Skies</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/bountiful-fares\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bountiful Fares</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/chipped\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Chipped</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/cobblemon\" rel=\"nofollow\">Cobblemon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://curseforge.com/mod/croptopia\" rel=\"nofollow\">Croptopia</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/deep-aether\" rel=\"nofollow\">Deep Aether</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/deeperdarker\" rel=\"nofollow\">Deeper and Darker</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/dreamwoods\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dreamwoods</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/dynamictrees\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dynamic Trees (+ Addons)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/ecologics\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ecologics</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/enderscape\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Enderscape</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/ends-phantasm\" rel=\"nofollow\">En